2001-12-27  Martin Junius  <mj@m-j-s.net>

	======= Release 4.4.5 ================================================
	------- CVS tag R445 -------------------------------------------------
	------- CVS ci -------------------------------------------------------

	* build-rpms: dito.

	* cvsexp: use version script.

	* version: new script, print version number from version.h

	* README: moved important stuff to top ;-)

	* ANNOUNCE: updated.

	* fidogate.lsm: updated.

