	  config.pl and new %CONFIG_dosdrive, %CONFIG_zone.

	* config.pl (CONFIG_read): special treatment for DosDrive and Zone 
	  config statement, store in %CONFIG_dosdrive and %CONFIG_zone
	  hashes. 

