	======= Release 4.3.5 ================================================
	------- CVS tag R435a ------------------------------------------------
	------- CVS ci -------------------------------------------------------

	* sendmail/mklinks (DIRS): create DIRS if needed.

	------- CVS tag R435 -------------------------------------------------
	------- CVS ci -------------------------------------------------------

